  <brief_title>The Impact of Using Triclosan-antibacterial Sutures on the Incidence of Surgical Site Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;The Impact of Using Triclosan-antibacterial Sutures on the Incidence of Surgical Site Infection&quot; Prospective, Randomized, Controlled, Double Blind, Multi-centre Study.</official_title>
