  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare conventional polyglactin 910 sutures with triclosan-coated polyglactin 910
      antimicrobial sutures for the reduction of surgical site infections and any associated health
      and economic benefits.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
